with
the
sacred
Table
of
Planetary
Hours.
The
hour
ofYanor
is
blue.
The
hour
ofNasnia
is
red.
The
hour
ofSalam
is
white.
Now
was
the
hour
of
Caerra,
meaning
the
light
in
the
room
had
modulated
to
a
soft
